data.description: Looking for an affordable roomy house with a huge shop? This Bremerton Gem is close to PSNS & Bangor. Cared for home has remodeled kitchen; easy-close cabinets, custom lighting, island, pot rack, SS appliances, 2021 Fridge, Vaulted ceiling, new laminate flooring, pellet stove, air conditioning window unit cools entire living area. Freshly painted throughout. Double sink guest bath. Den/office a third bedroom? Primary has custom wood built-ins-updated bath new vanity. Fully fenced w/2 plum, 2 apple, 2 types of cherry, 2 weeping willow trees, fish pond, 3 patios, Lg coop can be converted to workshop w/outlets 2B connected. 28 x 28 shop! RV, cars, and/or boats. Front spacious covered deck, flowering plants & bulbs to bloom yearly.
